\c 8
\s Dhavhidhi anokunda VaFirisitia nedzimwe ndudzi
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika pashure, kuti Dhavhidhi wakarova VaFirisitia ndokuvaisa pasi \add pake\add*; Dhavhidhi ndokutora Metegama kubva muruoko rweVaFirisitia.
\v 2 Zvino wakarova Moabhu, ndokuvayera nerwonzi, avaradzika pasi; uye nerwonzi ruviri wakayera kuuraya, uye nerwonzi rwakazara kuchengeta upenyu. VaMoabhu ndokuva varanda vaDhavhidhi vachiuya nezvipo.
\p
\v 3 Dhavhidhi wakarovawo Hadhadhezeri mwanakomana waRehobhu mambo weZhobha, pakuenda kwake kunodzosa ushe hwake parwizi Furati.
\v 4 Dhavhidhi ndokutapa kubva kwaari vatasvi vemabhiza churu nemazana manomwe, nevaifamba netsoka zvuru makumi maviri; Dhavhidhi ndokugura marunda emakumbo emabhiza ese engoro, asi wakasiya paari ngoro zana.
\v 5 VaSiriya veDhamasiko pavakauya kuzobatsira Hadhadhezeri mambo weZobha, Dhavhidhi wakauraya varume zvuru makumi maviri nezviviri zveVaSiriya.
\v 6 Dhavhidhi ndokuisa mapoka evarwi muSiriya yeDhamasiko; VaSiriya ndokuva varanda vaDhavhidhi vachiuya nezvipo. Jehovha ndokuchengetedza Dhavhidhi pese paakaenda.
\v 7 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakatora nhovo dzegoridhe dzaiva dziri pavaranda vaHadhadhezeri, ndokudziunza kuJerusarema.
\v 8 Mambo Dhavhidhi wakatorawo ndarira zhinji kwazvo paBheta nepaBherotai maguta aHadhadhezeri.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Toi mambo weHamati wakanzwa kuti Dhavhidhi waiva arova hondo yese yaHadhadhezeri,
\v 10 Toi ndokutuma mwanakomana wake Joramu kuna mambo Dhavhidhi kumubvunza upenyu nekumurumbidza nokuti waiva arwisa Hadhadhezeri ndokumurova (nokuti Hadhadhezeri waiva wehondo naToi); uye muruoko rwake maiva nemidziyo yesirivha nemidziyo yegoridhe nemidziyo yendarira.
\v 11 Naiyo mambo Dhavhidhi wakaitsaurira Jehovha pamwe nesirivha negoridhe yaaiva atsaura kubva kundudzi dzese dzaaiva aisa pasi \add pake\add*;
\v 12 kuVaSiriya, nekuVaMoabhu, nekuvana vaAmoni, nekuVaFirisitia, nekuVaAmareki, nekuzvakapambiwa zvaHadhadhezeri mwanakomana waRehobhu mambo weZobha.
\v 13 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakaita zita paakadzoka pakurova VaSiriya paMupata weMunyu, vaiva \add varume\add* zvuru gumi nezvisere.
\p
\v 14 Zvino vakaisa mapoka evarwi paEdhomu; wakaisa mapoka evarwi paEdhomu yese; vese veEdhomu vakava varanda vaDhavhidhi. Jehovha ndokuchengetedza Dhavhidhi pese paakaenda.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakatonga pamusoro paIsraeri wese; Dhavhidhi ndokuita zvakaenzana nekarurama kuvanhu vake vese.
\v 16 Zvino Joabhu mwanakomana waZeruya waiva pamusoro pehondo, naJehoshafati mwanakomana waAhirudhi waiva munyori.
\v 17 Zvino Zadhoki mwanakomana waAhitubhi naAhimereki mwanakomana waAbhiatari vaiva vapristi, naSeraya waiva munyori.
\v 18 Zvino Bhenaya mwanakomana waJehoyadha \add waiva pamusoro\add* peVaPereti, uye vanakomana vaDhavhidhi vaiva vabati.
